social_posts.post_text: New one out today for the boy. Preciate u @morganwallen for doin ur thing on this one and makin me even more proud of it than the day @blakemccoypendergrass @driverwilliams and I wrote it. Thank u guys for lettin me be part in writin this hammer w y'all. Love all boys 🫶🏽 days that end in why out now.
Had a blast writin this w @sarahsteilmusic and @casey_smith - big congrats on the release fam! 🤞🏽🤞🏽
Last night out w the boys @charliehandsom3 @jkash and #ashleygorley - @morganwallen u croonin' sob, preciate u brother
@chaserice thank u for lettin me be part of this special project, been excited for the world to get to hear the real raw u - biggest congrats my brother!

Incredibly proud to be a part of this record. @morganwallen preciate u brother for doin what u do for all us and makin us feel like it means somethin. 

Love all my co-writers who helped write these w me, love all my big loud peeps who got it to where it is. Will always appreciate all u guys. And thank God for givin me a life that me 10 years ago was dreamin about. 

Y'all check out this new album ya boys got these ones on there.

Honestly still tryna process this - there's a million things I could say rn but I'll just keep it short and say this for real one of the highlights of my life. 

Thank u first to my mom, dad, stepdad, siblings, and rest of my family that's always had my back. Wouldn't be no where close without yall. Thank u mike g for bein one of my best friends and teammates. Love u bro. Seth n Joey, preciate y'all believing in this song - and morgan love u my man thank u for everything. Unbelievable. 

Kash, ash, charlie - love u gang...WE UP!! 

Thank u God for my first number one.
unreal to have a legend like @leannrimes hop on this song w @tenillearts that we were already so proud of, big preciate everyone who made this happen!

first time I heard jamo's voice on this in @garciaofficial's studio I teared up a lil bit. tru story lol. thanks for makin me proud of this one u two. we knew we caught magic the day @ifiwerehillarylindsey @chris_lacorte and I wrote it - preciate u gang and everyone else that had a hand in makin this happen!

tagged one w my boys @andrewalbert @zdevin and @durrett.tv - @larryfleet thank u for connecting w this song enough to record it, we appreciate u brother. if u grew up country go check this one. cmon young buck

lil piece for the fellas - wrote this w @tphillipsmusic @charliehandsom3 #smashlygorley n @dylanscottcountry himself. preciate u lovin this song as much as I do bro!

Ps shoutout to @durrett.tv & @charliehandsom3 on killin the production
congrats @laurenalaina on the new project n thank u for lettin me be a part of it 🫶🏽 wrote "hangovers" w the boys @joshosbornesongwriter @greylanjames @mattroylive!

big thanks to @iamchasematthew for lovin n livin this song enough to put it on his new album - the music vid is crazy go check it out. wrote "blink" w @blakemccoypendergrass @durrett.tv @jordanminton and @tphillipsmusic gangs on patrol

been waitin on this one for 2 and half yrs but was well worth it - loved writin "Hey Can I Buy You a Beer" w @rockyblock and @traviswoodcoolguy back in feb of '21. @jakeowenofficial u killed it my guy congrats on the new album y'all go check out the whole thing called "Loose Cannon" he out nowww

fun lil joint i'm not crazy by @charlieonnafriday out now 😵‍💫

3rd floor boys are 🆙🆙 preciate the gang @jordandozzi @dirty615 & @rockyblock for gettin up on a random afternoon in the flex room to make this and preciate @durrett.tv for producin it for dirt and as always big thanks to @dylanscottcountry for killin it and makin it a hit love you fellers
